      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>Initial Release</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Area, window, and fullscreen capture</li>
          <li>Smart crop with Vision saliency detection</li>
          <li>OCR text extraction (searchable history)</li>
          <li>Annotation tools (arrows, rectangles, highlights)</li>
          <li>Pin screenshots as floating overlays</li>
          <li>Markdown and citation clipboard formats</li>
          <li>Customizable hotkeys</li>
          <li>4 built-in presets for common workflows</li>
        </ul>
